b3f91c30cb784e8f5a16b","modified":1769955102245},{"_id":"themes/hydrogen/source/css/_katex.css","hash":"c6e1c9608daa0c38aacdfdf8a31045d38507acd7","modified":1769954271371},{"_id":"themes/hydrogen/scripts/markdown.js","hash":"97d0258f54579a4de4c3167869d51f11ea86893f","modified":1769955156352}],"Category":[],"Data":[],"Page":[{"title":"关于我","_content":"\n$$\ny = kx = b\n$$\n\n## 自我介绍\n\n我叫Frish2021，也可以叫Frish或者Fr，我还有另外一个名字叫CoderFrish，来自广东的一名学生，今年高中一年级。\n\n### 名字由来\n\n关于我的名字的由来，是大概小学五年级的时候想着开一台自己的Minecraft服务器（后面没开成，改成写Minecraft服务端了/doge），后面写了个叫Minecraft开服协议书，上面的署名就是潦草的\nFrish2021,当时年份是2021年，所以直接Frish + 2021了，感觉也算是个标记吧。后面叫Fr完全是Frish的简写，Frish是Frish2021的简写，相比来说叫我Frish的人比叫我Fr的人还多，因为叫我\nFr的就一位哥们。\n\n### 擅长\n\n我没什么擅长的，纯宅家废人一个，也就是写写代码什么的（看过游戏代码，但是游戏还玩的贼菜的人/doge）。\n\n### 学过的编程语言\n\n我学习编程最早从小学三年级开始接触Python。六年级正式开始玩实战用java，以下是我再学习路程上学过的编程语言（包括高级语言和脚本语言以及汇编）\n\n| Java       | Python     | C      | C++      |\n|------------|------------|--------|----------|\n| C#         | Kotlin     | Groovy | Assembly |\n| Go         | JavaScript | Rust   | PHP      |\n| TypeScript | Lua        |        |          |\n\n### GitHub Status\n\n<div style=\"display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\">\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CoderFrish/CoderFrish/master/generated/overview.svg\" alt=\"\"/>\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CoderFrish/CoderFrish/master/generated/languages.svg\" alt=\"\">\n</div>\n","source":"about/index.md","raw":"---\ntitle: 关于我\n---\n\n$$\ny = kx = b\n$$\n\n## 自我介绍\n\n我叫Frish2021，也可以叫Frish或者Fr，我还有另外一个名字叫CoderFrish，来自广东的一名学生，今年高中一年级。\n\n### 名字由来\n\n关于我的名字的由来，是大概小学五年级的时候想着开一台自己的Minecraft服务器（后面没开成，改成写Minecraft服务端了/doge），后面写了个叫Minecraft开服协议书，上面的署名就是潦草的\nFrish2021,当时年份是2021年，所以直接Frish + 2021了，感觉也算是个标记吧。后面叫Fr完全是Frish的简写，Frish是Frish2021的简写，相比来说叫我Frish的人比叫我Fr的人还多，因为叫我\nFr的就一位哥们。\n\n### 擅长\n\n我没什么擅长的，纯宅家废人一个，也就是写写代码什么的（看过游戏代码，但是游戏还玩的贼菜的人/doge）。\n\n### 学过的编程语言\n\n我学习编程最早从小学三年级开始接触Python。六年级正式开始玩实战用java，以下是我再学习路程上学过的编程语言（包括高级语言和脚本语言以及汇编）\n\n| Java       | Python     | C      | C++      |\n|------------|------------|--------|----------|\n| C#         | Kotlin     | Groovy | Assembly |\n| Go         | JavaScript | Rust   | PHP      |\n| TypeScript | Lua        |        |          |\n\n### GitHub Status\n\n<div style=\"display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\">\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CoderFrish/CoderFrish/master/generated/overview.svg\" alt=\"\"/>\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CoderFrish/CoderFrish/master/generated/languages.svg\" alt=\"\">\n</div>\n","date":"2026-02-01T14:11:42.245Z","updated":"2026-02-01T14:11:42.245Z","path":"about/index.html","_id":"cuidHaaql6gh_tc98ehH-MV2Z","comments":1,"layout":"page","content":"<p><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>k</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>b</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">y = kx = b\n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03148em;\">k</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">b</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<h2 id=\"自我介绍\">自我介绍</h2>\n<p>我叫Frish2021，也可以叫Frish或者Fr，我还有另外一个名字叫CoderFrish，来自广东的一名学生，今年高中一年级。</p>\n<h3 id=\"名字由来\">名字由来</h3>\n<p>关于我的名字的由来，是大概小学五年级的时候想着开一台自己的Minecraft服务器（后面没开成，改成写Minecraft服务端了/doge），后面写了个叫Minecraft开服协议书，上面的署名就是潦草的<br>\nFrish2021,当时年份是2021年，所以直接Frish + 2021了，感觉也算是个标记吧。后面叫Fr完全是Frish的简写，Frish是Frish2021的简写，相比来说叫我Frish的人比叫我Fr的人还多，因为叫我<br>\nFr的就一位哥们。</p>\n<h3 id=\"擅长\">擅长</h3>\n<p>我没什么擅长的，纯宅家废人一个，也就是写写代码什么的（看过游戏代码，但是游戏还玩的贼菜的人/doge）。</p>\n<h3 id=\"学过的编程语言\">学过的编程语言</h3>\n<p>我学习编程最早从小学三年级开始接触Python。六年级正式开始玩实战用java，以下是我再学习路程上学过的编程语言（包括高级语言和脚本语言以及汇编）</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Java</th>\n<th>Python</th>\n<th>C</th>\n<th>C++</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>C#</td>\n<td>Kotlin</td>\n<td>Groovy</td>\n<td>Assembly</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Go</td>\n<td>JavaScript</td>\n<td>Rust</td>\n<td>PHP</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>TypeScript</td>\n<td>Lua</td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"GitHub-Status\">GitHub Status</h3>\n<div style=\"display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\">\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CoderFrish/CoderFrish/master/generated/overview.svg\" alt=\"\"/>\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CoderFrish/CoderFrish/master/generated/languages.svg\" alt=\"\">\n</div>\n","excerpt":"","more":"<p><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>k</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>b</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">y = kx = b\n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03148em;\">k</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">b</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<h2 id=\"自我介绍\">自我介绍</h2>\n<p>我叫Frish2021，也可以叫Frish或者Fr，我还有另外一个名字叫CoderFrish，来自广东的一名学生，今年高中一年级。</p>\n<h3 id=\"名字由来\">名字由来</h3>\n<p>关于我的名字的由来，是大概小学五年级的时候想着开一台自己的Minecraft服务器（后面没开成，改成写Minecraft服务端了/doge），后面写了个叫Minecraft开服协议书，上面的署名就是潦草的<br>\nFrish2021,当时年份是2021年，所以直接Frish + 2021了，感觉也算是个标记吧。后面叫Fr完全是Frish的简写，Frish是Frish2021的简写，相比来说叫我Frish的人比叫我Fr的人还多，因为叫我<br>\nFr的就一位哥们。</p>\n<h3 id=\"擅长\">擅长</h3>\n<p>我没什么擅长的，纯宅家废人一个，也就是写写代码什么的（看过游戏代码，但是游戏还玩的贼菜的人/doge）。</p>\n<h3 id=\"学过的编程语言\">学过的编程语言</h3>\n<p>我学习编程最早从小学三年级开始接触Python。六年级正式开始玩实战用java，以下是我再学习路程上学过的编程语言（包括高级语言和脚本语言以及汇编）</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Java</th>\n<th>Python</th>\n<th>C</th>\n<th>C++</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>C#</td>\n<td>Kotlin</td>\n<td>Groovy</td>\n<td>Assembly</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Go</td>\n<td>JavaScript</td>\n<td>Rust</td>\n<td>PHP</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>TypeScript</td>\n<td>Lua</td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 id=\"GitHub-Status\">GitHub Status</h3>\n<div style=\"display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; justify-content: center;\">\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CoderFrish/CoderFrish/master/generated/overview.svg\" alt=\"\"/>\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/CoderFrish/CoderFrish/master/generated/languages.svg\" alt=\"\">\n</div>\n"},{"title":"标签","layout":"tags","_content":"","source":"tags/index.md","raw":"---\ntitle: 标签\nlayout: tags\n---\n","date":"2026-01-09T16:27:13.829Z","updated":"2026-01-09T16:27:13.829Z","path":"tags/index.html","comments":1,"_id":"cuidCuY7MSH5xrFb4BCqzQJ7e","content":"","excerpt":"","more":""}],"Post":[{"title":"Hello World","_content":"Welcome to [Hexo](https://hexo.io/)! This is your very first post. Check [documentation](https://hexo.io/docs/) for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in [troubleshooting](https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html) or you can ask me on [GitHub](https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues).\n\n## Quick Start\n\n### Create a new post\n\n``` bash\n$ hexo new \"My New Post\"\n```\n\n$$\ny = kx + b\n$$\n\nMore info: [Writing](https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html)\n\n### Run server\n\n``` bash\n$ hexo server\n```\n\nMore info: [Server](https://hexo.io/docs/server.html)\n\n### Generate static files\n\n``` bash\n$ hexo generate\n```\n\nMore info: [Generating](https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html)\n\n### Deploy to remote sites\n\n``` bash\n$ hexo deploy\n```\n\nMore info: [Deployment](https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html)\n","source":"_posts/hello-world.md","raw":"---\ntitle: Hello World\ntags: \n  - test\n  - hello\n---\nWelcome to [Hexo](https://hexo.io/)! This is your very first post. Check [documentation](https://hexo.io/docs/) for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in [troubleshooting](https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html) or you can ask me on [GitHub](https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues).\n\n## Quick Start\n\n### Create a new post\n\n``` bash\n$ hexo new \"My New Post\"\n```\n\n$$\ny = kx + b\n$$\n\nMore info: [Writing](https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html)\n\n### Run server\n\n``` bash\n$ hexo server\n```\n\nMore info: [Server](https://hexo.io/docs/server.html)\n\n### Generate static files\n\n``` bash\n$ hexo generate\n```\n\nMore info: [Generating](https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html)\n\n### Deploy to remote sites\n\n``` bash\n$ hexo deploy\n```\n\nMore info: [Deployment](https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html)\n","slug":"hello-world","published":1,"date":"2026-01-31T12:22:48.564Z","updated":"2026-02-01T14:08:33.681Z","_id":"cuid47edx3PNVu9YrMmOBvE_g","comments":1,"layout":"post","photos":[],"content":"<p>Welcome to <a href=\"https://hexo.io/\">Hexo</a>! This is your very first post. Check <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/\">documentation</a> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html\">troubleshooting</a> or you can ask me on <a href=\"https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues\">GitHub</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"Quick-Start\">Quick Start</h2>\n<h3 id=\"Create-a-new-post\">Create a new post</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo new <span class=\"string\">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mrow><mi>y</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>k</mi><mi>x</mi><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">y = kx + b\n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.625em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">y</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7778em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03148em;\">k</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">x</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">b</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html\">Writing</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Run-server\">Run server</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/server.html\">Server</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Generate-static-files\">Generate static files</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html\">Generating</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Deploy-to-remote-sites\">Deploy to remote sites</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html\">Deployment</a></p>\n","excerpt":"","more":"<p>Welcome to <a href=\"https://hexo.io/\">Hexo</a>! This is your very first post. Check <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/\">documentation</a> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html\">troubleshooting</a> or you can ask me on <a href=\"https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues\">GitHub</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"Quick-Start\">Quick Start</h2>\n<h3 id=\"Create-a-new-post\">Create a new post</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td